{"tid":2139153,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新砌機 嗶五下 黑畫面求救！","createTime":"2020-08-04T05:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T14:18:19.000Z","uid":223947,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"91c252d22d1dd33868d48b12852eb39e85294a48","tid":2139153,"uid":223947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"第一次砌機<br />\n上網搵過哂啲方法都唔work 唔知邊度出左問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n底板有燈 有著風扇 <br />\n拎走左顯示卡黎試<br />\n試過重插ram卡 13、24、12、34槽 單槽<br />\n試過拎走粒電仔5分鐘再開機<br />\n試過重裝舊cpu<br />\n以為係bios唔support舊cpu <br />\n<br />\n拎過塊板底同cpu 去維修睇 佢幫我整完bios 係現場佢又開到喎<br />\n（佢係用我塊板同粒cpu 但無用我舊cpu風扇）<br />\n點知返到屋但重組後情況都無變<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以打救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用緊AMD B450m steel legend 底板<br />\nR7 ryzen 3800x cpu <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a6080df39307658d44d3826a0758b1de0803e6","tid":2139153,"uid":6374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"火牛幾多power?<br />\nDisplay card？"},{"pid":"ccf92efb39176b87dffaf8f49b515aa68a5c1013","tid":2139153,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"full spec?"},{"pid":"34c00e2b35f6757f140d533538cab4b6e899ff01","tid":2139153,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"逐樣試囉<br />\n攞最低限嘅插住開機先(RAM、CPU)，睇下有無畫面出先，再逐樣加插上去<br />\n至少佢幫你試咗塊板同cpu無事"},{"pid":"7d72f7e45b1ae7b175bb983330ade711429ff9c3","tid":2139153,"uid"